videos.description: Georgetown's Terrell Allen drives into the lane and passes over the top to Omer Yurtseven, who flushes it home to complete the alley-oop connection.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Allen lobs to Yurtseven for Georgetown alley-oop) 2020/01/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Allen lobs to Yurtseven for Georgetown alley-oop

videos.description: Saddiq Bey drives, draws two Georgetown defenders and dishes to a wide-open Brandon Slater under the hoop for an easy two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Slater left wide open for Villanova slam) 2020// ESHEET

videos.headline: Slater left wide open for Villanova slam
